    "description": "Glob is a fast-paced platformer that really <i>swings</i> into action! Use your gooey sling to pull yourself around, or use it to throw obstacles at enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting sling mechanic</h2>Master your sling as you use it to fly through levels at a blistering pace! The sling allows you to grab onto both terrain and various objects, most likely leading to you flying into a saw blade at first! Once you master the sling, you'll move around levels like a real glob!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/f6b531aa9570e79637462c1245720909.poster.avif?t=1697009465\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/f6b531aa9570e79637462c1245720909.webm?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/f6b531aa9570e79637462c1245720909.mp4?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smash your Friends</h2>Race your friends in the time trials or compete in a deathmatch to see who has the fastest sling! Online high scores and matchmaking ensures you'll always have a whole glob of fun!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/e7054924285822182780e7857158e1e3.poster.avif?t=1697009465\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/e7054924285822182780e7857158e1e3.webm?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/e7054924285822182780e7857158e1e3.mp4?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PvP and Coop</h2>Exciting levels which challenge your platforming and slinging skills as you try to overcome each level by yourself or with friends. It's up to you if you want to be able to sling your friends as you progress through the levels, leading to hilarious moments of betrayal.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/a757fe87e0d8e234000133acdd86d456.poster.avif?t=1697009465\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/a757fe87e0d8e234000133acdd86d456.webm?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/a757fe87e0d8e234000133acdd86d456.mp4?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Something for everyone</h2>Many varying game modes to cater for everyone - Capture the Flag, Competitive Racing, Arena Battle, Cooperative Puzzles, and more! Group up in teams or try your luck as a lone glob.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/9b7e084833753aab1f08c24e791bf867.poster.avif?t=1697009465\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/9b7e084833753aab1f08c24e791bf867.webm?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/9b7e084833753aab1f08c24e791bf867.mp4?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Daring leaps and bounds</h2>Featuring gripping sections of daring jumps and swings, you'll need to overcome many challenges to succeed. Did we mention there are lasers?!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/35f06792bc70c81330826a7d277c8127.poster.avif?t=1697009465\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/35f06792bc70c81330826a7d277c8127.webm?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898980/extras/35f06792bc70c81330826a7d277c8127.mp4?t=1697009465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
